  "liveNow": false,
  "panels": [
    {
      "gridPos": { "h": 7, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Node Auto-Provisioning (NAP) — elastic Spot CI nodes\nGKE **Node Auto-Provisioning** is the GA, Google-native equivalent of Karpenter. The `ci-spot` **Custom ComputeClass** ([`infrastructure/compute-classes/ci-spot.yaml`](../infrastructure/compute-classes/ci-spot.yaml)) makes NAP auto-create **Spot, scale-to-zero** node pools for bursty CI build agents (Spot-first c3/n2/c2/e2 → on-demand fallback). The long-lived platform stays on the **static** `jenkins-2026-pool`. See [`docs/201`](../docs/201-ARCHITECTURE.md) and [`docs/501`](../docs/501-PLATFORM_OPERATIONS.md).\n\n**How to read it:** watch **Spot nodes** rise when a pipeline build starts and fall back toward **0** a few minutes after it finishes (consolidation) — that is the scale-to-zero cost profile. The **Static pool** line should stay flat (the platform). *No data?* It reads node taints from kube-state-metrics (`kube_node_spec_taint`); `03-observability.sh` keeps that tiny node-inventory slice even in lean/free-tier mode, so check KSM is up (`kube-state-metrics` pod) and that a build has actually triggered a Spot node."
      }
    },
    {
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 7 },
      "id": 2,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Total nodes",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "color": { "mode": "thresholds" }, "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [{ "color": "green", "value": null }] }, "unit": "none" }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "area", "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false }, "textMode": "auto" },
      "targets": [
        { "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" }, "editorMode": "code", "expr": "count(kube_node_info)", "legendFormat": "nodes", "range": true, "refId": "A" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 7 },
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Spot CI nodes (NAP)",
      "description": "Nodes labelled cloud.google.com/gke-spot=true — the ephemeral capacity NAP provisions for the ci-spot ComputeClass.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "color": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "orange" }, "unit": "none" }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "area", "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false }, "textMode": "auto" },
      "targets": [
        { "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" }, "editorMode": "code", "expr": "count(kube_node_spec_taint{key=\"cloud.google.com/gke-spot\"}) or vector(0)", "legendFormat": "spot", "range": true, "refId": "A" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 12, "y": 7 },
      "id": 4,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "ci-spot ComputeClass nodes",
      "description": "Nodes auto-created for the ci-spot Custom ComputeClass (GKE auto-labels them cloud.google.com/compute-class=ci-spot).",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "color": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "purple" }, "unit": "none" }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "area", "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false }, "textMode": "auto" },
      "targets": [
        { "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" }, "editorMode": "code", "expr": "count(kube_node_spec_taint{key=\"cloud.google.com/compute-class\",value=\"ci-spot\"}) or vector(0)", "legendFormat": "ci-spot", "range": true, "refId": "A" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 18, "y": 7 },
      "id": 5,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Static platform nodes",
      "description": "Non-Spot nodes — the long-lived jenkins-2026-pool hosting ArgoCD/Jenkins/observability/CNPG.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "color": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "green" }, "unit": "none" }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "area", "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false }, "textMode": "auto" },
      "targets": [
        { "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" }, "editorMode": "code", "expr": "count(kube_node_info) - (count(kube_node_spec_taint{key=\"cloud.google.com/gke-spot\"}) or vector(0))", "legendFormat": "static", "range": true, "refId": "A" }
      ]
    },
    {
